{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"129126-a-translated-title-in-english-would-be-rabbit-the-chef-rather-than-the-original-nuance-as-this-would-translate-in-japanese-better-and-in-a-more-natural-way","title":"ウサギのシェフ","description":"あさごはんに、なまのニンジン。おひるごはんとばんごはんにも、なまのニンジン。ウサギは、なまのニンジンにあきてしまったので、おいしいニンジンカレーをつくるほうほうをかんがえます。","language":"Japanese","langCode":"ja","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Jun Goto"],"illustrators":["Chamath Prasanga Lokuliyana"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/129126-a-translated-title-in-english-would-be-rabbit-the-chef-rather-than-the-original-nuance-as-this-would-translate-in-japanese-better-and-in-a-more-natural-way"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/105036/size3/18f8fd4a121fc54acd71d658d4013da8.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/105036/size6/18f8fd4a121fc54acd71d658d4013da8.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75109/size6/d7852db038112530226f80bc511d6173.jpg","text":"「わたしは、まいにちニンジンをいっぽんたべます。」ウサギはいいました。","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75110/size6/7ea92a1351cf79e5a3c607555aeb0002.jpg","text":"「なまのニンジンは、もうあきた！」","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75111/size6/6c09b4a0879bc768a7723dc40e6d40cf.jpg","text":"「どうしたら、このニンジンをおいしくできるかな？」","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75112/size6/5652eae4fc57ede6ea42fa8fc3a31c38.jpg","text":"ゆうがたに、ウサギはあるのうかのおうちにいきました。ウサギは、ひのうえでグツグツにえているおなべをみました。","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75113/size6/34fa4ee3def2cc4b6322fc52b4526e6c.jpg","text":"ウサギがあるアイデアをおもいついたとき、のうかのイヌがとびだして、ウサギにほえてきました。","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75114/size6/49585906913abf40f362287807eefc2f.jpg","text":"「んー。」ウサギはかんがえました。\n「さあ、なにをしようかな？」","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75115/size6/820e709f5a62b70ba4c603720f0e4a3b.jpg","text":"ウサギは、ニンジンをたいようのひざしにあてました。\nでも、ニンジンはなまのままです。","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75117/size6/44889d693ef5ce0d50db022021815cb5.jpg","text":"ウサギは、ニンジンをひにあてました。\n　　　　　\n　　　　　　ウサギは、ニンジンをかじりました。\n　　　　　　にがい！","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75118/size6/dacab5fa1b93ac1b681279114584ceff.jpg","text":"ウサギは、どうすればいいのか、ずっとかんがえました。","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75119/size6/ffddd85db5a2c059e4aa403e8cde851b.jpg","text":"ついに、ウサギはアイデアをおもいつきました！\nウサギは、カメのこうらをみつけました。","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75120/size6/66d6676568df57ad27fc11ac0d3e90b0.jpg","text":"そのあと、きをあつめました。","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75121/size6/83af7793713cbc3f8fc68fa8e680b1a4.jpg","text":"みっつのいしもあつめました。","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75122/size6/e35ad5dbab7820fd4785965ab2ce424a.jpg","text":"やったあ！\nウサギは、やっとニンジンをりょうりできるようになりました。","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75123/size6/26e3080ff22efd06438d18b714fb1e44.jpg","text":"ウサギはとてもうれしかったので、ともだちをみんなよびました。","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/75124/size6/5993fdf5cf5895db8ecdca89cd5d583f.jpg","text":"ウサギは、みんなとおいしいニンジンのおりょうりをたべました。","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":21}}